OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,FMore than 70% of people, including a
OL,7,Fmajority of Leave voters, agree that
OL,8,FBrexit has been more of a failure than
OL,9,Fa success in Northern Ireland, an
OL,10,Fopinion poll has suggested.
OL,12,FThe results of the research from
OL,13,FQueen's University Belfast also
OL,14,Findicate two-thirds of people in the
OL,15,Fregion believe Brexit has made the
OL,16,Fbreak-up of the UK more likely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
