OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778803375
OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,FThe polling, carried out for Queen's
OL,7,Fby LucidTalk, suggests that close to
OL,8,Fhalf of voters (48%) do not agree that
OL,9,Fthe 2016 Brexit referendum was based
OL,10,Fon a "fair democratic process", while
OL,11,F40% agree.
OL,13,FThe report is the 15th in the "Testing
OL,14,Fthe Temperature" series on Northern
OL,15,FIreland voters' views on Brexit and
OL,16,Fthe Northern Ireland Protocol/Windsor
OL,17,FFramework, led by Professor David
OL,18,FPhinnemore and Professor Katy Hayward.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@^O]uD@_OUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
