OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,FPrevious reports were produced as part
OL,7,Fof a four-year project led by Queen's
OL,8,Fand funded by the Economic and Social
OL,9,FResearch Council.
OL,11,FThis latest poll was conducted between
OL,12,FApril 17-20, using a weighted sample
OL,13,Fof 1,050 respondents from across
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,16,FThe survey found declining public
OL,17,Funderstanding among respondents of the
OL,18,FWindsor Framework, the post-Brexit
OL,19,Fdeal between the UK and the EU aimed
OL,20,Fat reducing trading frictions between
OL,21,FGreat Britain and Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
