PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778803375
OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,FPoll findings included:
OL,8,F` 72% of respondents agree that
OL,9,F"Brexit has been more of a failure
OL,10,Fthan a success for Northern Ireland".
OL,11,FThis includes 60% of Leave respondents.
OL,13,F` 66% agree that Brexit has made the
OL,14,Fbreak-up of the UK more likely; 19%
OL,15,Fdisagree.
OL,17,F` More than twice as many agree (52%)
OL,18,Fthan disagree (23%) that their Brexit-
OL,19,Frelated identity, Leaver or Remainer,
OL,20,Fis "very important" to them.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@dO]|D@DOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
