OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,F` 46% of respondents now regard the
OL,7,FWindsor Framework as "on balance a
OL,8,Fgood thing for Northern Ireland", the
OL,9,Flowest level since June 2021, while
OL,10,F38% disagree.
OL,12,F` Confidence in the NI Protocol/
OL,13,FWindsor Framework as a tool for
OL,14,Fmanaging Brexit's effects has
OL,15,Fdeclined, with only 46% now viewing it
OL,16,Fas an appropriate means of addressing
OL,17,FBrexit in Northern Ireland, down from
OL,18,F61% in summer 2024 and equal to its
OL,19,Fprevious low recorded in spring 2021.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
