OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778803375
OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,F` Views among respondents of the
OL,7,Fframework's effects on Northern
OL,8,FIreland's relationship with the rest
OL,9,Fof the UK remain negative, including
OL,10,Fon its place in the UK internal market
OL,11,F(44% negative vs 28% positive).
OL,13,F` Perceptions of the Windsor
OL,14,FFramework's economic impact are more
OL,15,Fpositive than negative, 45% believe it
OL,16,Fhas had a positive effect on the
OL,17,Feconomy, while 37% believe its impact
OL,18,Fhas been negative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
