SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778803375
OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,F` A majority of respondents (57%)
OL,7,Fbelieve the Windsor Framework offers
OL,8,Funique economic opportunities, down
OL,9,Ffrom 68% in summer 2024.
OL,11,F` A majority distrust either a
OL,12,FConservative-led (76%) or Reform-led
OL,13,FUK government (70%) to protect
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland's interests in EU-UK
OL,15,Frelations.
OL,17,F` The SDLP is the most trusted party
OL,18,Famong respondents on the Windsor
OL,19,FFramework (38%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
