OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,F` The TUV the most trusted unionist
OL,7,Fparty (30%) on the issue, though it is
OL,8,Falso the most strongly distrusted
OL,9,F(50%).
OL,11,FProf Phinnemore said: "The poll
OL,12,Fprovides further evidence that
OL,13,Funderstanding of the Windsor Framework
OL,14,Fis declining.
OL,16,F"In part, this is no doubt due to the
OL,17,Fcomplexity of some of its arrangements.
OL,19,F"Yet the poll findings also show fewer
OL,20,Fvoters believing reliable information
OL,21,Fis available.
OL,26,@sD@WOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
