OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,F"With the UK and EU negotiating new
OL,7,Fagreements that are expected to reduce
OL,8,Ftrade frictions arising from the
OL,9,FWindsor Framework, it will be
OL,10,Fimportant that the new arrangements
OL,11,Fare clearly and reliably explained.
OL,13,F"If they are not, then this will only
OL,14,Ffurther damage trust levels in the UK
OL,15,FGovernment and the EU."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
