OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,FProfessor Hayward said: "Ten years
OL,7,Fafter the Brexit referendum, one in
OL,8,Ftwo voters in Northern Ireland still
OL,9,Fsee their Leave/Remain identity as
OL,10,Fvery important ` across both camps and
OL,11,Fthe political spectrum.
OL,13,F"This constitutes an additional layer
OL,14,Fof division broadly on top of existing
OL,15,Fones.
OL,17,F"The need to manage this with
OL,18,Fcompromise on both sides explains the
OL,19,Fregion's unique post-Brexit
OL,20,Farrangements, ie the Windsor Framework.
OL,26,@nD@YOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
