PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778803375
OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,F"It also helps explain why the
OL,7,Fmajority of both Leavers and Remainers
OL,8,Fhere believe ` albeit for different
OL,9,Freasons ` that Brexit has been a
OL,10,Ffailure for Northern Ireland."
OL,12,FThe survey also suggested a preference
OL,13,Famong voters for closer ties with the
OL,14,FEU ` 59% of respondents oppose further
OL,15,Floosening of UK-EU ties and 57%
OL,16,Fsupport the UK rejoining the EU, with
OL,17,Fstrong gender and Remain/Leave divides.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
