OL,3,CLarge majority in Northern Ireland see
OL,4,CBrexit as a failure, poll suggests
OL,6,FAlmost three-quarters (73%) of
OL,7,Frespondents support Ireland using its
OL,8,FEU Council Presidency to improve EU-UK
OL,9,Frelations.
OL,11,FMore than half of respondents (58%)
OL,12,Foppose leaving the European Convention
OL,13,Fon Human Rights while 36% support such
OL,14,Fan exit.
OL,16,FThe poll has a margin of error of +/-
OL,17,F2.3%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
